1094
00:56:40,708 --> 00:56:42,208
- He does!
- Yeah.

1095
00:56:42,292 --> 00:56:44,458
He does. He sucks.

1096
00:56:44,542 --> 00:56:49,083
He calls me "Al," and he's 30 years old,
and he waxes his armpits.

1097
00:56:49,167 --> 00:56:52,500
- Hey, I told you that in confidence.
- [Alex chuckles]

1098
