1121
00:58:06,625 --> 00:58:07,625
[Alex grumbles]

1122
00:58:10,708 --> 00:58:14,542
- I'm the king of the world!
- That is not better than "Seabiscuit."

1123
00:58:16,750 --> 00:58:18,500
- Here we go!
- No! No, no, no!

1124
00:58:18,583 --> 00:58:19,792
