- Okay.

1155
00:59:23,042 --> 00:59:24,583
Are you…? Can I…?

1156
00:59:24,667 --> 00:59:26,500
- Don't touch me. Don't touch me.
- Okay.

1157
00:59:26,583 --> 00:59:28,375
- Okay.
- Sorry. Thank you.

