And Sarah.

1187
01:00:43,583 --> 01:00:44,583
[Alex] Mm…

1188
01:00:45,083 --> 01:00:48,750
Can we maybe talk about this
when I'm in a little less pain?

1189
01:00:48,833 --> 01:00:49,958
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

1190
01:00:50,042 --> 01:00:51,542
[serene music plays]

1191
