1235
01:02:57,042 --> 01:02:58,875
I'm so sorry, Alex.

1236
01:02:59,375 --> 01:03:02,083
Don't be. Really. Uh…

1237
01:03:03,292 --> 01:03:04,833
Just feel better.

1238
01:03:06,708 --> 01:03:09,333
Just get on that plane, Alex.

1239
01:03:09,417 --> 01:03:10,417
